thread.title: Five Questions for Thursday’s European Central Bank Meeting

author: Tom Fairless
title: Five Questions for Thursday’s European Central Bank Meeting

organizations.name: european central bank meeting the european central bank

text:
The European Central Bank could be enjoying a rare period of calm, after announcing a major reduction of its stimulus in October. Instead, the bank’s top officials have started squabbling publicly over their next move.

The reason for the dispute is the eurozone economy, which is in its strongest shape in more than a decade. Some officials...
